code: @Override public StringBuilder getHdfsPath(HdfsConfiguration config) {     StringBuilder hpath = new StringBuilder().     hpath.append("file://").     hpath.append(config.getPath()).     if (config.getSplitStrategies().size() > 0) {         hpath.append('/').     }     return hpath. }

@Override public StringBuilder getHdfsPath(HdfsConfiguration config) {     StringBuilder hpath = new StringBuilder().     hpath.append("hdfs://").     hpath.append(config.getHostName()).     hpath.append(':').     hpath.append(config.getPort()).     hpath.append(config.getPath()).     if (config.getSplitStrategies().size() > 0) {         hpath.append('/').     }     return hpath. }
